{"type":null,"faqId":34606,"title":"系统休眠后，数据业务是否会自动断开？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.22222222in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>是的。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如需使数据业务一直保持连接，请参考如下步骤：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置 &gt; 更多 &gt; 移动网络”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-1</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110382\" style=\"width:5.046528in;height:3.879861in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击或滑动“始终连接数据业务”后的开关至 “</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110383\" style=\"width:0.28541666in;height:0.20625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >图1-2</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110384\" style=\"width:2.6875in;height:3.9916666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=110385\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":3,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9347","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436866855000,"seriesProductName":"M2-801w,M2-803L","visitedTimes":83,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"休眠,系统休眠,熄屏,数据业务,移动网络,网络断开,网络连接 ,自动断开","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}